  "title": "feat(connectHierarchicalMenu): update getWidgetSearchParameters",
  "body": "This PR updates the lifecycle `getWidgetSearchParameters` in `connectHierarchicalMenu` to add the configuration of facets and default value. We don't apply the previous value on purpose, the `uiState` drives completely the `SearchParameters`.\r\n\r\nI've not removed the `getConfiguration` lifecycle (yet) to avoid breaking everything. Once we've made the switch to `getWidgetSearchParameters` we'll remove them.",
